INSTALL:

Unpack the archive into a directory, put your own settings into BotConfig.hs
then run:

	autoconf
	./configure
	make	(gmake on some systems)

KNOWN BUGS:
* @topic often returns nothing, no idea why

Bug reports, patches, new modules etc, contact:

